\f0\b\fs28 Overview\

\f1\b0\fs24 \
WAVsToAAF scans your WAVs, extracts production metadata (BEXT, RIFF LIST-INFO, embedded XML), auto-tags with UCS categories, and builds real AAFs. Use linked media for lightweight bins and easy relink, or embed audio for self-contained handoffs \u8211  your choice per run.\
\

